Class SmallMap<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.garret.perst.PinnedPersistent
      • org.garret.perst.Persistent
        • org.garret.perst.PersistentResource
          • org.garret.perst.SmallMap<K,V>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Externalizable, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.util.Map<K,V>, ICloneable, ILoadable, IPersistent, IResource, IStoreable

    public class SmallMap<K,V>
extends PersistentResource
implements java.util.Map<K,V>
    This class provide small embedded map (collection of <key,value> pairs). Pairs are stored in the array in the order of their insertion. Consequently operations with this map has linear ccomplexity.
